title: 258. #75HARD vs Carlos Reyes vs Sal Frisella
itunes:title: 258. #75HARD vs Carlos Reyes vs Sal Frisella
description: In today's episode, Andy is joined in the studio by Real Estate Entrepreneur Carlos Reyes and 1st Phorm President Sal Frisella to discuss their #75HARD experiences. They dive deep into the triggers that led them to start the program, how it has positively impacted their relationships with family & friends and why it's crucial to invest in your mental discipline.
